      <prop type="x-translation-ref">狡童.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼狡童兮，不與我言兮，維子之故，使我不能餐兮。
彼狡童兮，不與我食兮，維子之故，使我不能息兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>That artful boy !
He will not speak with mef
But for the sake of you, Sir,
Shall I make myself unable to eat ?
That artful boy !
He will not eat with me !
But for the sake of you, Sir,
Shall I make myself unable to rest ?</seg>
      </tuv>
